  "detailed_description": "Pumpkin Dog Xtreme is a 3D platformer inspired by 3D platforming games from the 90’s.<br />\r\nUnique Retro soundtrack, over 24 levels and a boss battles and bonus stages.<br />\r\nThe game has a large amount of different levels and large number of enemies.<br />\r\nPlay as 2 characters, Pineapple Dog and Pumpkin Dog.<br />\r\nPineapple Dog has a fisheye lens.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:<br />\r\n-Controller Support<br />\r\n-Genre, 3D Platformer<br />\r\n-Boss Battles<br />\r\n-Low poly 3D environment<br />\r\n-over 24 stages<br />\r\n-Bosses<br />\r\n-Special Stages<br />\r\n-Fisheye Lens",
